_sText:
I'm proud to release the first version of my second submitted map! Tears went into this map, and I could not be happier to submit the result to the public!
This map is based on dynamic events that change up the map a tad bit. More events will be added in feature versions.

Please not this is not the finished result, as this map took about 2 weeks to make. You are guaranteed to find something ugly in this map. If you do come across something unbearable, please let me know.

Have fun.
